metadata.description:
0xPhapes is the very first Phunk collection from the PhunkyVerse consisting of 10.000 distinct Phapes. Owning this genesis piece gives you a free mint and voting rights for every new Phunk addition to the PhunkyVerse. All additional mints you choose to do will fund the PhunkyVerse treasury.

STAY PHUNKY.

 Join our community in the [Discord](https://discord.gg/4qjVjUHKpx)/r/n/r/n Follow us on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/0xPhapes_) for more details.
